Start a node (of any type).
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]stop\f[]
Stop a node.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]restart\f[]
Restart a node.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]run\f[]
Run a node synchronously.
.RS
.RE
