.TP
.B \f[B]-C,\ --basedir=\f[]
Same as \[em]node-directory.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]-d,\ --node-directory=\f[]
Specify which Tahoe node directory should be used (default for most
commands: `$HOME/.tahoe/').
.RS
.RE
.TP
